snippet.title: Super Mario 64 - The Missing Stars: Part 1
snippet.description:
Super Mario 64 - The Missing Stars
Part 1 - Main City Area

In the first part we cover the 6 stars of the Main City Area, activate the Wing Cap switch and get the secret star.

Ahh, Yoshi was so annoying in this. It would be the time when I get bad luck from him, but whatever, it all went fine except some stupid mistakes (Wow this sounds like I'm evaluating a speedrun).

As a side note, there is no commentary as I do not do single person commentary. On time of recording this, nobody was online to talk to. In future parts I may have co-commentators, depending on whether I feel like it.
Also the quality of the video isn't great, but I'm not re-uploading this. I will be messing around with Fraps settings and the game graphics to make the quality better, so in future parts it should be better.

This is a custom Super Mario 64 Hack made by Messiaen aka 'Frauber'.
Link to his Site: https://sites.google.com/site/messiaen64/
Link to his YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/frauber
Go to this games playlist: http://goo.gl/lQkJa

Comments are enabled so you can post constructive criticism, otherwise I'll disable them again, pretty much same with voting.
